info.description: Teagarden is a django based webapplication used for database planning and modelling during the software development process. With Teagarden, software developers and database architects can create database tables, fields, constraints and relations without specifying the database system they want to use for their project. Teagarden aims to be a database development platform and documenation tool, but can also create the final SQL statements and compares the specific, productive database against the modelling metadata schema.
info.name: django-teagarden
info.summary: Database planning, visualization and code generation
